body.name: Convertible Baby Stroller, Foldable Pushchair, Newborn Reversible Bassinet Pram with Adjustable Canopy, Aluminum Structure, 5-Point Harness for Infant & Toddler
deliveryMessages: Or fastest delivery Tomorrow, February 17. Order within 5 hrs 48 mins
features: 2 In 1 Bassinet Stroller：baby stroller for newborns can be used as a baby carriage stroller and bassinet stroller for babies 0-36 months. The baby basket can be adjusted in two modes. When the basket is facing the parents, the parents can easily take care of the baby at any time and pay attention to the baby's movements. With the basket facing out, your baby can enjoy the scenery and interaction outside.

Multi-Functional Practical Baby Carriage:1. Bassinet strollers are equipped with detachable foot covers to withstand the cold winter winds and provide a warm and comfortable environment for your baby. 2. A storage basket under the seat is ideal for storing groceries, diaper bags, and baby supplies. 3. Five-point seat belts keep your baby safe at all times.

Aluminum Alloy Structure and Foldable Design: The baby carriage stroller is made of ultra-light aluminum alloy, which is very strong and stable. our stroller uses breathable Oxford fabric, which protects your baby from rain or harmful rays. In addition, the folding design of the infant stroller, bassinet pram, and reversible newborn bassinet pram is very convenient for storage and carrying, and you can fold the toddler stroller in just a few seconds.

Adjustable Canopy & Backrest: Convertible stroller you can adjust the height of the seat according to your preferences, and adjust to a comfortable Angle for your baby to rest. By adjusting the backrest, the cradle can be divided into three modes: sitting, semi-reclining, or sleeping mode, to meet the different needs of the baby. Three-stage canopy design can be adjusted according to different weather conditions, well prevent strong sunlight for the baby to provide the best rest environment.

Durable All-Terrain Anti-Shock Wheels: Four wheels adopt an advanced shock-absorbing design with strong damping springs, making the stroller available for multiple kinds of roads. The front wheel with lock can either go straight or 360° rotate to your needs. And the rear wheels are designed with a brake for emergent stops.
